  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of the study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of SPRC-AB01 versus
      placebo for treatment of chronic sinusitis in subjects who have had sinus surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
